download cuda from nvidia
shutdown the gui service: sudo service lightdm stop
goto cmdline mode: ctrl+alt+1
 \t if cannot get in cmdline mode, update grub file: sudo gedit /etc/default/grub
 \t replace "quiet splash" with "nomodeset"
sudo sh <the cuda filename>
follow all the instructions and do not install opengl library
then add cuda to environment path(see docs on nvidia)


or:
sudo apt-get install nvidia-cuda-toolkit,might not working
